{"tid":507649,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[醜陋真相] 15年未帶兒子外出食聖誕大餐的父親","createTime":"2017-12-23T13:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T13:26:56.000Z","uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0453a587c92f5f86824aac29de542f7544a456","tid":507649,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"明報明益你，悲慘中產的幸運兒陳基棠 <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.littleoslo.com/cnt/home/wp-content/uploads/2011/12/winner-531x800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.littleoslo.com%2Fcnt%2Fhome%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2011%2F12%2Fwinner-531x800.jpg&h=ae16e09a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信是2017年最後一個笑話了，由今天明報副刊頭條報導「15年最溫馨大餐」的「新聞」掀起，其實不過是鱔稿一篇，酒店送獎品，你出版面，讀者又得益，三贏局面的宣傳，皆大歡喜，透過文章更可一睹香港中產悲慘的一面，原來就是：「15年來，幾乎從沒帶兒子外出食聖誕大餐，希望給兒子一個特別難忘的聖誕。」 <br />\n<br />\n幾乎從沒，即係有吃過啦，不過重點是這次「夢想成真」的幸運兒陳基棠一家三口的慘況，報導表示，包括要供一層位於港島東七百多呎自住單位 (疑似康怡花園)，先生是銀行電腦部System Manager，太太是認證機構秘書，小康之家月入數萬，僱有家傭，惜上有高堂供養，下有獨子照顧，要請兩名補習老師，加上學習長笛及參加童軍活動，生活的重擔讓他們覺得「錢總是不知所終」，以致「每年最多只能與兒子食自助餐一兩次，並選擇價錢較低廉的午餐時段」，至於較平時貴幾成的聖誕大餐，對他們一家來說是過於奢侈的消費：「一家三口連車費，動輒數千。」 <br />\n<br />\n聞者心酸，見者流淚，所以明報是次活動統籌一鋒明言：明益你「夢想成真」收到很多來信，首先多謝讀者支持。信中看到每人有不同夢想，雖然今次只可為兩名讀者圓夢，但希望其他人能堅持追夢，正如我選擇陳家，也是希望讓社會上不同人士也繼續擁抱夢想，不要放棄，只要堅持到底，夢想一定可成真。祝願大家在2018年心想事成。"},{"pid":"6b3d5222937ad4523ab90377c5cc25de486111aa","tid":507649,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:04:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa3d053f91a5351f4dd17159cb4a74649142140","tid":507649,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6735a005909e33e35f5c1a5086fab8e5907178a6","tid":507649,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2567f58dcb4877bad81a83e4b5e1220321e580e0","tid":507649,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7dfee98d58fe64679aa9e33462e88639637ff71","tid":507649,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933aa60808032938a1ee77780c7c47257337cb05","tid":507649,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:13:56.000Z","msg":"幫你推下"},{"pid":"42f19de988ed5daadc46697870b7fd5196afea8c","tid":507649,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:20:18.000Z","msg":"屌你月入加埋十萬<br />\n住港島要R報紙請"},{"pid":"775e1f21fc7cb2220610b2bd791a6d3508daa221","tid":507649,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:20:20.000Z","msg":"嘩慘到呀"},{"pid":"05983cc293eecb092aeef026b041666e227abd6e","tid":507649,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T13:26:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}